# Contributing to the Ping Pong Method Project

Thank you for considering contributing to the Ping Pong Method project! Your input is valuable in improving and refining this framework.

## How to Contribute

### **1. Fork the Repository**

- Click the **"Fork"** button at the top-right corner of the repository page to create a copy in your GitHub account.

### **2. Clone the Repository**

- Clone the forked repository to your local machine:

  ```bash
  git clone https://github.com/matkowsky/PingPongMethod.git
